Package: nvcr
Type: Package
Title: Package for the United States National Vegetation Classification
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jacob", "Malcom",
                  email = "jmalcom@defenders.org",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Data from the United States National Vegetation Classification
    (NVC) database, available from http://usnvc.org/explore-classification/.
    This packages includes all tables from the database as data.frames; a set of
    pre-joined tables that seem most useful; and document-term matrics (DTMs)
    from feature definitions.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.3)
License: BSD_2_clause + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Imports:
    dplyr,
    RSQLite
